tch_gamepage_header-3000x900.png", "id": "281783280932651", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75422375_281783284265984_2262616227321638058_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lk4NEESNlrQQ7kNvgEgrXen&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBuzAqcRwYhFSP-LA2KXx4BEfUzrY5jD2FRYReJ2e-D3A&oe=66F67EC1"}, {"file_name": "itch_gamepage_header_wide-1080x360.png", "id": "150576644686961", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982610_150576648020294_8694113331780370751_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0eTahnf-MKoQ7kNvgHYHTct&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBpLhCsl_dr8sgCLkAwoxOXlfhPYSZP_1lJV78DebkDmg&oe=66F6B56C"}]}, "id": "2478600158983510", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "scr_1.png", "id": "782428473283391", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974471_782428476616724_1116172443318779459_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=m_xzPSa3l7cQ7kNvgGpeuEK&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQ8VBW5L3pgCKzZ2IFaWVakkWSEvn941WVUlSS1xM1yQ&oe=66F686D1"}, {"file_name": "scr_4.png", "id": "159298223794289", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031624_159298230460955_160499850208589564_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dsaEx9D0_3MQ7kNvgF1dBK9&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAiy2LYBx2ALt1iPlVegQWOMANMhPzTdjCVf099599VQg&oe=66F68E9D"}, {"file_name": "scr_3.png", "id": "1622890074875818", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003228_1622890078209151_210179435196440368_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Rlpzu171BUQQ7kNvgEBJlHT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDBDfM_63z0OTzxv7_UEdK27Rl9V4bj3wj-lSCrEeJFag&oe=66F68179"}, {"file_name": "scr_2.png", "id": "177703811915843", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003228_177703815249176_1528287960455225088_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yO5mCQy3cW0Q7kNvgEsnBSU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAVUBnlk-vzGmknoisAr13Et8T9DWQPlqjlV2WxtTjOgA&oe=66F6A80A"}, {"file_name": "scr_5.png", "id": "808935813774196", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031332_808935817107529_8861221418933832083_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jrMr-UsGFJcQ7kNvgEj1jD8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDAB-TIKWF0Nn-dqnwe_ggjy1sCeT8cqEaoXa5U4zLWtg&oe=66F6A8DC"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The king is gone", "keywords": [], "long_description": "In this game, you have to run away. Different doors are blocking the way, that need to be unlocked to proceed as fast as possible. Each door will give a different benefit, and a combination of them is the key to succeed .. or fail.\n\nTo open a door, a puzzle is presented, where pieces of a key have to be rotated and merged together to open the door. The further you run, the more difficult the key puzzles become.\n\nThere are three different modes:\n\n* Normal Mode: Score is increasing the more you survive. It decreases the more you stay idle in a room without picking a door. There's a set amount of rooms to complete before reaching the end.\n* Endless Mode: Score increases with each room that is completed. There is no end to the amount of rooms presented.\n* Random Mode: Each door has a specific score as a reward when opened. Rooms and their rewards spawn at random.\n\nThe available benefits from the doors are:\n\n* Green doors: Increase running speed.\n* Purple doors: Increase lock-picking skills, which makes opening new doors easier.\n* Blue doors: Gives extra chances before losing.\n* Brown doors provide no direct benefit, apart from helping complete more rooms.", "short_description": "A puzzle game about running, not because one has somewhere to be, but because one has somewhere they don't want to be."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://afloofdev.com/privacy_policy/games/", "developer_terms